eu.itesla_project.iidm.network

Interface SubstationAdder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdentifiableAdder<SubstationAdder>

    public interface SubstationAdder
extends IdentifiableAdder<SubstationAdder>
    To create a substation, from a Network instance call the Network.newSubstation() method to get a substation builder instance.

    Example: 

        Network n = ...
    Substation s = n.newSubstation()
            .setId("s1")
            ...
        .add();
    Author:
    Geoffroy Jamgotchian
    See Also:
    Substation, Network
